name: MyPersonalFitnessTrainer
0:
”Alexa, open my personal trainer”
”Alexa, start my personal trainer”
”Alexa, ask my personal trainer to start workout”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my personal trainer
des: Work out with Alexa throughout the week. Once you open the skill, just ask Alexa to start the workout. There are plenty of workouts ranging in difficulty and length so you can find the workout for you and your busy schedule. Alexa can even motivate you! Who needs a real personal trainer when you've got Alexa!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
